Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.39,0:00:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.01,0:00:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個充滿神秘的黑暗組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法想通的不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.74,0:00:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在哪裏存在提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小五郎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.43,0:01:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送在網上加入"魔術愛好者聯盟"的園子和小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到雪山的度假別墅參加聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在返程的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說"魔術愛好者聯盟"的聊天室室長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西山務被人殺害在自己傢中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.82,0:01:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場還有留言表明將要發生連續殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們匆忙回去想要接小蘭她們回來 可是面前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是熊熊燃燒的吊橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.92,0:02:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我一個人到達了度假別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因爲感冒發起了高燒 生了重病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後接著是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個犧牲者出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麽可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.81,0:02:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 濱野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.11,0:02:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來也沒用 他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.91,0:02:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 別破壞現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.04,0:02:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的屍體距離別墅超過10公尺以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.92,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是週圍只有剛才跑過去的土井塔的腳印而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 這樣就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個案子的確是沒有翅膀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所無法犯下的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.99,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術愛好者殺人事件(疑惑篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽是濱野先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽非殺了他不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個道理我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.98,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能確定他是被人勒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手應該是利用類似細繩之類的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他的脖子勒住窒息而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用某種方法把他的屍體運到這來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這名兇手就在這個別墅的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，你該不是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名殺人兇手就在我們幾個人之中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒沒這麽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在在這裏的就只有我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.65,0:04:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了涉嫌的應該還有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認爲他很可能就躲在什麽地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認爲這個人可能性非常的高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的這個人是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天晚上本來也預定到這來過夜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.00,0:04:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這個“魔術愛好者聯盟”的其中一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“影法師”不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子倒是可以說得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自傢房裏被發現的西山務屍體旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.81,0:04:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是留下了類似這樣的一句留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的意思是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在說不定就在什麽地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著取我們的性命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麽玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，田中小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中小姐，你要幹什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這個別墅裏面有個殺人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回不去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我回到這裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座唯一的吊橋就已經被人放火燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽 沒有那座吊橋的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就根本沒有辦法下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道電話線也是兇手切斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們還有手機可以用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.05,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.09,0:05:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏已經超出通信範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們已經被這名兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的和下面的世界給隔離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道“影法師”的真正身份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎，警部大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真面目這還很難說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們知道他是”魔術愛好者聯盟”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個成員就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要從他的身分證就可以查出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本是另外一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.46,0:05:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人跟魔術根本沒有任何的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去這兩年也從來沒有接觸過電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是上過網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.23,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人擅自利用他的護照或者是身份資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.53,0:06:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再以“影法師”的身份上網和網友溝通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，現在還不止這一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.61,0:06:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在那個渡假別墅裏還有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是利用神秘的身份和其他網友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行溝通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一開始讓濱野表演餘興節目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是濱野沒有一個人關在房間裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他也不會遇害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都是因爲被我選中了才會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.15,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你根本不用放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是被蒙著眼睛，隨機抽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨意選擇了三張卡片在上面做上記號的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿射飛鏢的遊戲來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.59,0:07:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果會拿到什麽禮物沒理由怪射飛鏢的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一樣的道理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天只是幫濱野的魔術做了助手而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你根本沒有什麽道理好自責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.11,0:07:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子幫他的魔術做助理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有沒有問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大傢這麽悠閑的在這裏等救兵行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊橋被燒的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔正好在橋的對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他立刻就去找警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們乖乖待在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想天亮以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定就會跟警方的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏來救我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.57,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果兇手真的是“影法師”的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.77,0:07:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看之前的chat應該就是原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽chat啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的chat就是以電腦利用電話線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.72,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在處理係統上進行多人交談的一種專有名詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖然說是在交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是利用出現在屏幕上的文字進行交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟殺人有什麽關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們曾經爲了某個魔術師起了爭執嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.97,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該聽過過去一個名字叫做春井風傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.54,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號稱是“日本逃生大王”的老魔術師吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.24,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是上個月在表演的時候意外身亡的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.35,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們大傢討論那場意外的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.29,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“影法師”卻突然說了一句很奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說 那位偉大的魔術師之所以會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你們害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前我們在chat上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.17,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於過去風行的”逃生秀”討論的非常起勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來就說到應該找個人來表演才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後意外就發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以“影法師”就說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是因爲我們討論那個話題的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也未免扯太遠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了謹慎起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經跟聊天室的室長西山確認過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說在半年前的chat裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有像春井的這麽一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.56,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說大傢輸入的身份資料不一定是本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.73,0:09:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經讓什麽人看過這段對談的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟西山討論了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會計劃了今天的這一次聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些參加對談半年以上的人聚集起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接確定資料總是比較快嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.02,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“影法師”是最近才入會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎麽知道半年以前的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是想嚮他本人確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是爲了解除誤會才會找他一塊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 影法師平時常會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要飛天去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是我能夠讓你們隨時消失無蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說這個兇手就是“影法師”的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.51,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽今天的不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就可以解釋的過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是當著我們的面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演了一場血淋淋的魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣溫好像降下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.16,0:10:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我到房間裏去拿件衣服披著好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也跟你一起去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想拿件毛衣什麽的給他穿在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣我也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多一點總是比較安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.15,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽連進個房間都變得膽顫心驚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦，這件衣服太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南,不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.16,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了,園子姐姐幫忙做助手表演魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.03,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.99,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲濱野先生說要分配工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採用魔術的方式來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後決定代理室長是黑田小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責燒洗澡水的田中小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於餘興節目就由濱野先生負責了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.54,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說濱野先生會一個人待在房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因爲要準備餘興節目嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回房間就是要想要表演什麽魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候其他人在做什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有他們分配的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭，快點好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“影法師”說不定正在什麽地方伺機而動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.01,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“影法師”這個傢夥真的是兇手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有一個人見過他的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢的不在場證明也很暧昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個兇手會把我們困在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是還想再搞什麽鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.45,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會讓他得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他更別想要殺什麽人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.16,0:12:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭…箭突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰，快給我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.85,0:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離窗戶遠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子，園子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟黑田小姐在廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽到浴室那裏傳來玻璃破的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子就到那裏看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭直接射進了鏡子裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從那邊進來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說來有人想從外面攻擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麽玩笑，真的把我惹火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，田中小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要畏首畏尾的躲著,快給我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹林裏面全都是腳印耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說真的有人躲在樹林裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.70,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽是我們碰上這種事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.41,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個該不會是，十字弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該很清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示兇手絕對不是我們之中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了現在大傢都沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兇手就把十字弓丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.97,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.76,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，這次的聚會差勁透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不該來這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用怪這個聚會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也許可以心平氣和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.27,0:14:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我呢 剛才十字弓直接威脅我的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺你能懂嗎琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之，還是先回屋裏去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裏太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱野先生真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣被丟在雪地裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是該給他蓋張牀單什麽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他屍體週圍的雪地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有留下任何一個人的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是不可能犯罪最明確的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽完美的藝術品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽能夠容你們用腳印來加以破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽藝術有沒有搞錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看這不是十字弓的箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那些箭是用來對付我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是運氣不好的話我們說不定也犧牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們還是先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這棵樹的週圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有積在樹枝上的雪掉下來的蹟象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹幹上竟然開了一個新的洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是剛才誰惡作劇挖出來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然還是徘徊在這附近的誰挖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目的又是什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.97,0:15:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.04,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是剛才一直有可疑舉動的這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土井塔克樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.18,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱野被殺的時候我們在做什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.38,0:16:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我在睡覺所以才想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你問這種事情要做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是認爲我們之中有人就是兇手對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的箭是從外面飛進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連十字弓也是在樹林裏面被發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麽說兇手應該是另有其人才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在誰都沒有看過兇手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽快就下結論未免太早了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.98,0:16:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是趁現在弄清楚比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想濱野被殺害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.28,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是在他待在房間裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黑田小姐一直待在餐廳裏面排餐具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了稍後的晚會做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧，黑田小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.96,0:16:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，排好餐具之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就到了廚房裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始幫須嫌做準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荒先生要我到廚房準備幾道菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那黑田阿姨跟須嫌叔叔在廚房的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.47,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土井塔叔叔在做什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我就到房間去拿我爲晚會準備的餅幹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿餅幹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我爲了看柯南的病況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.35,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就往小蘭的房間去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來園子邀請我過來吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把柯南留在房間裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起下樓到客廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我是到酒窖去拿酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我被分派到燒洗澡水的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在用柴火燒熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段期間，大概花了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.01,0:17:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛，大概是7-8分鍾左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概也用了這麽多的時問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過確切時間就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概8分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲在荒先生回到客廳來這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好在使用烤箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.82,0:17:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到酒窖裏面去拿酒就要花8分鍾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.73,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因爲我完全忘了酒窖已經裝了新鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還到房裏去拿鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝了新鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你要不要直接去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 上面這兩個鎖就是新裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶，裝了好多的鎖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽需要這麽多鎖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲之前這裏有小偷進來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才多加了幾道鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.22,0:18:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我們這唯一值錢的就只有這些酒而已了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔，那是廚房的後門嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的腳印怎麽特別多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到這裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.40,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢曾經一起把這棟別墅週圍繞過一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那個時候留的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了小弟弟，這樣過瘾了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回屋子裏去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再順便看看燒洗澡水的地方嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是燒水的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小屋的頂上面好像沒有積什麽雪嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因爲燒水的時候溫度會阩高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雪都滑下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔，那是哪裏的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是二樓走廊盡頭的那面窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說只要爬上屋頂就能到二樓去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對，田中阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.74,0:19:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯不過不只我一個人爬上去過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我爲了了解熱水燒得情況怎麽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還曾經去浴室那裏看了2-3次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，你這是什麽意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要趁我不在的時候到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都有機會爬上去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一被十字弓的箭射穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有浴室的這面窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上面田中小姐屋內的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從兇手射箭的角度來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在剛才我們所在的那片森林裏才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中小姐的屋內有人影晃動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手射箭進來還沒話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.15,0:19:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他幹嘛射沒有人的浴室呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麽，是釘書針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會掉在這兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成這會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.05,0:20:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查進行得怎麽樣了，小偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，大傢都進屋裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼頭還是一樣喜歡到處亂晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱野叔叔決定大傢分配工作的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以詳細的告訴我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子我已經大致了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的謎題只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.75,0:21:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能解開這個謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能將兇手找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他是怎麽做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體週圍半徑10公尺之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪地上一片雪白沒有一個腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是利用起重機將屍體舉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從空中放下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓誰做都不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得站在屍體週圍的哪個柱子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽想都想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢來喝杯酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體會暖和點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候還喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只喝一點沒什麽關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能稍微緩解一下心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，原來是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.77,0:21:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪兇手要把那座吊橋燒掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.80,0:21:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們跟山下的世界隔離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完全看穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不可能犯罪的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.75,0:22:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下這宗罪行的是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.34,0:23:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是柯南的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.25,0:23:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,大傢一起上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.80,0:24:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.68,0:24:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.32,0:24:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是在右邊的樹林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.47,0:24:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.27,0:24:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術愛好者殺人事件(解決篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.16,0:24:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.84,0:24:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十字弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.55,0:24:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集終於是解決篇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.50,0:24:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也會出來哦
